    "faq_pTh7RC": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "faqs_4A7UM9": {
          "type": "faqs",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is Pillowta?",
            "answer": "<p>Pillowta is a space being created for people who want intimacy to feel human again - slow, honest, and unforced.<br/>We are building a culture before we build a product.<br/></p>",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "faqs_ACWFQw": {
          "type": "faqs",
          "settings": {
            "title": "When will Pillowta officially launch?",
            "answer": "<p>We’re taking our time to get it right.<br/>The launch will be announced first inside our private <strong> </strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScYsgphJ_CP0xm8K1hwlBx6DI94dnZtzfc6ncEmIhJw8cskMw/viewform\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScYsgphJ_CP0xm8K1hwlBx6DI94dnZtzfc6ncEmIhJw8cskMw/viewform\"><strong>community</strong></a><strong>. </strong><br/></p>",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "faqs_H4n7kp": {
          "type": "faqs",
          "settings": {
            "title": "You’re already closer than you think.",
            "answer": "<p>Join our<a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send/?phone=917683866116&text=Here%2C+with+intention&type=phone_number&app_absent=0\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send/?phone=917683866116&text=Here%2C+with+intention&type=phone_number&app_absent=0\"><strong> WhatsApp Community</strong></a> to receive early stories, behind-the-scenes moments, and first access when we go live.<br/>Follow us on our social pages, where the story of Pillowta unfolds quietly, one moment at a time.<br/></p>",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "faqs_pdfWCd": {
          "type": "faqs",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Will I be the first to know when Pillowta opens?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes.<br/>Those who walk with us now will be the first to step inside when the doors open.</p>",
            "open": false
          }
        }
      },
